          SHORT="nss_ldap provides NSS services for LDAP"
cat << EOF
The resolution of the entities defined in RFC 2307
is generally performed by a set of UNIX C library
calls (such as getpwnam() to return the attributes of a user).
The nss_ldap module provides the means for workstations
to this information (such as users, hosts, and groups)
from LDAP directories.
EOF

